{"tid":262972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Bosco純真無機心     野戰會會長轟疑犯太兇狠","createTime":"2017-05-29T15:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T17:02:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60b874aeb14dc7cae58de77a6bb119bb89a06560","tid":262972,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:26:49.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496068561_25fa.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496068561_25fa.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=Q6RggPcQhaOQXSxgmALDlE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e9ec095c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496068561_25fa.jpg%5B%2Fimg&h=9ef87a86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496068561_25fa.jpg[/img</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170529/large/1496068563_3b2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170529%2Flarge%2F1496068563_3b2c.jpg&h=446ad1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被誘到山上打Wargame而遇害的20歲青年郭葦諾(Bosco)，約3年前加入野戰會「Silent Knight（靜默騎士）」。該會會長Frankie在Bosco失踪後一度上山協助搜索，未料最終傳來噩耗，他感到痛心難過，直指Bosco為人樂觀、純真及沒有機心，指摘疑兇「諗唔到佢哋咁兇狠，可以對個小朋友落手(殺害Bosco)！」<br />\n<br />\nFrankie指Bosco約3年前加入野戰會，首次活動就是穿上軍服為該會拍攝封面照，因而雙方認識；之後Bosco也經常參與聯誼活動，亦出席打野戰活動。Bosco較鍾情模仿美國陸軍特種部隊游騎兵(United States Army Rangers)，惟他體力不佳，在隊中主要負責支援角色，喜愛購買裝備為主，已買齊全套裝備落場。而Bosco對上一次是在本月21日參加元朗的Wargame對戰，其間他從未透露因買裝備與人結怨。<br />\n<br />\nFrankie形容Bosco為人樂觀、純真及無機心。Frankie因Bosco年紀較少，往往以大哥哥身份就工作及裝備上提供意見，更曾勸喻Bosco購買裝備適可而止，切勿過度消費，而Bosco亦會接納意見。Frankie直指不認識案中3名疑兇，亦從無參加對方活動，想不到Bosco遭毒手，批評：「諗唔到佢哋(疑犯)咁凶狠，可以對個小朋友落手！」Frankie擬聯合會員計劃籌募帛金，向郭家提供經濟援助。"},{"pid":"cec76ee3b411be0ebfe7c989d27256da4b4211a7","tid":262972,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"敗類"},{"pid":"b11e29d4bc0591376a50280cdf5df43390dbf3c5","tid":262972,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"個團名咁中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eeb815a725d67c8d9c226d2625633fb5ec3993f","tid":262972,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0dc823e6f898433096f533807c7feaba153203ef","tid":262972,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個團名咁中二<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改呢d公會名係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9785e2a5a267278c9045cd0c469980da138781d9","tid":262972,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 口舌招尤就比人殺 唔排除見佢學生哥就劏佢搵佢笨 死者之後唔服氣四圍講"}]}